- statistics
    you can select the range, [Today, Last 60 Days] per day
        for each meal
            [admins, regular users][accepted, rejected, pending] badges
        members
        badges


// statistics display
    - pie chart that shows accepted badges, declined and pending for a given period of time
        1 day, 7 days, 30 days, 60 days
    - same period before you get cards, each card represents a meal, with its name, start/end date
        number of accepted and declined badges same pie chart inside of it
    - a line that shows the number of accepted or declined badges over 1 week, 30 days, 60 days

// export
you set a period of time and download the last 1 day, 7 days, 30 days, 60 days
    in a csv format with each day and meals of that day and member count of that org at that day

